                    },
                    "body": "Nothing from what I can tell, just coded a little differently. The latest proposal skeleton class has the same features, and more. At least between the patch that I created, Zend_Log_Writer_Mail-Layout.txt.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=panman",
